eSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpaceEvent\"><code>XRReferenceSpaceEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRenderState\"><code>XRRenderState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRRigidTransform\"><code>XRRigidTransform</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSession\"><code>XRSession</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSessionEvent\"><code>XRSessionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSpace\"><code>XRSpace</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRSystem\"><code>XRSystem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRView\"><code>XRView</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewerPose\"><code>XRViewerPose</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRViewport\"><code>XRViewport</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLBinding\"><code>XRWebGLBinding</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLDepthInformation\"><code>XRWebGLDepthInformation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRWebGLLayer\"><code>XRWebGLLayer</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <strong><code>XRJointPose</code></strong> interface is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRPose\"><code>XRPose</code></a> with additional information about the size of the skeleton joint it represents.</p><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRPose\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      XRPose\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRJointPose\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"88\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"149\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      XRJointPose\n    </text>\n  </a></svg>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"xrjointpose.radius\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRJointPose/radius\"><code>XRJointPose.radius</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The radius (distance from skin) for a joint.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"using_xrjointpose_objects","title":"Using <code>XRJointPose</code> objects","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Call <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRFrame/getJointPose\"><code>XRFrame.getJointPose()</code></a> with an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRJointSpace\"><code>XRJointSpace</code></a> and an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a> to get an <code>XRJointPose</code> object.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>xr\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">requestSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">optionalFeatures</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"hand-tracking\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token comment\">/* … */</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">renderFrame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">session<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> frame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// …</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> inputSource <span class=\"token keyword\">of</span> session<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>inputSources<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>inputSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hand<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> indexFingerTipJoint <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> inputSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>hand<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"index-finger-tip\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      frame<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getJointPose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>indexFingerTipJoint<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> referenceSpace<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// XRJointPose</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Using XRJointPose objects"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"query":"api.XRJointPose","specifications":[]}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.XRJointPose","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRHand\"><code>XRHand</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRReferenceSpace\"><code>XRReferenceSpace</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRJointSpace\"><code>XRJointSpace</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRFrame/getJointPose\"><code>XRFrame.getJointPose()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The XRJointPose interface is an XRPose with additional information about the size of the skeleton joint it represents.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:23:40.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/xrjointpose","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/xrjointpose/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/073f70e052ff92ab715df3c20678c11c9b51747f","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XRJointPose","title":"XRJointPose"}],"pageTitle":"XRJointPose - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}